title: Gronk's Retirement, Russell Wilson, and Ranch Dressing
itunes:title: Gronk's Retirement, Russell Wilson, and Ranch Dressing
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company are back for a new episode of Benched with Bonnetta! Rachel is still broadcasting from Canada, where she's teaching her nephew how to eat pizza with ranch dressing. Gronk announced his retirement (again), so we tell our favorite Gronk stories as Rachel digs through keepsakes from her childhood. Russell Wilson explained why he chose the Broncos as his trade destination, and finally, we have our first TRIPLE elimination on this week's installment of the Benched Bachelorette.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
